column12: Suction nozzle for a vacuum cleaner
column13: The nozzle has two lateral sides (5, 6) forming a suction point and is open towards a surface that is to be cleaned by two suction channels (19, 20). The suction channels are arranged respectively along the length of each lateral side. Internal side of the nozzle has parallel scraper blades (45, 46), each extending from corresponding lateral side towards the other lateral side in the relative suction channel.
